Feels good to be able to do things up again, I’m back this time for good I know where I’m headed, my mind is clear, my goals are set 🙌🏻❤️

Weight has always been an issue for me since being kid, and over the years no matter how hard I’ve tried, i could lose weight but never fully maintain it! 

The last few years mentally have been challenging for me, and my weight has took the brunt of it. 

I got to a point where I was making constant excuses to everyone & myself. After trying every diet you could think of over the years, training as hard as I could train, I just couldn’t keep it off. 

Shockingly, last year I got to the biggest I’ve ever been, I knew it was time for me to make a serious decision about becoming a healthier person again. Not only for me but for my family & more importantly my little boy. 

My weight affected my sleep, my energy levels, my health, my singing & of course my confidence. 

So after a lot of research & seeing personal friends of mine go on this journey, And see it change their life I knew this was my time to embark on the same journey. So early January I had gastric sleeve surgery & honestly I feel like it’s already changed my life 🙌🏻❤️

I’m already over 2 1/2 stone down & I feel like a new man an my journey has only just begun….. 

It’s not just an operation, it’s a complete lifestyle change & you only get out what you put in 💪🏻 

I’m excited to share my journey with you all & hopefully make weight loss & gastric sleeve surgery not such a taboo subject 🫶🏻

#weightloss #gastricsleevesurgery #loosingweight #gastric #sleeve

Such a lovely evening at players lounge, Makes me so proud our little family open mic that has been running in essex over 30 years it’s still going today!!!

The atmosphere tonight was so old school I loved it!!! 

Now run by Dad & Char and still as busy as ever!!! I was looking around the packed room tonight being surrounded by over 20 singers and their families thinking about the 100’s that have come along over the years & some of our close family friends that have been with us since the start that still come to this day and their generations that follow in each others footsteps & get up and sing 👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻

It took me back to the good old days of the Belvedere!!! Such good times!!! I’m also still so lucky to see my mum and dad performing on stage they always amaze me & im so proud of both of them they are true pro’s I’ll never forget the foundations I learnt from them alongside so many other great singers that now takes me all over the world doing what I love every day of my life 🙌🏻❤️🫶🏻

These days I love showing Denny how I started in this business and singing his favourite songs and seeing him dance haha 

Great night next date will be released this week 🙌🏻❤️

Check out my journey 11 months on from my gastric sleeve 9stone down feeling amazing!!! FITTER - STRONGER - FASTER 💪🏻 from day 1 to my latest gym session today speed on my boxing is MAD 💨

Don’t worry 26st me could still pack a punch 🤣 but honestly I feel like a new man 3stone left till I finish this challenge & it’s now in touching distance 🙌🏻❤️🫶🏻

Thankyou to @getsliminturkey & @dr.fikretbeyaz for changing my life - I feel alive again - so much energy - buzzing to wake up and tackle every day & live life to the max🙏🏻

Thankyou to my pal & pt @maggsy_pt trained with this guy for many years he’s helped me through some hard times & has been a massive part in helping me achieving the shape, fitness & stamina again honestly mate your a top geezer! 

As I said before people think this op is a quick fix I can first hand tell you it’s not a walk in the park you have to still work your socks off if you want to achieve peak shape & fitness being able to only eat so much is just one part of it lol 

Lastly Thankyou to my wife & son my driving force behind the main reason I wanted to this time change my life forever there’s no going back, & this time I’m heading towards the best shape I’ve ever been in my life! 

Big up everyone else who’s been behind me every step of the way. Also big up everyone ether on the same journey as me or weight loss in general I’ve battled with this all my life I’ve been fat & slim again 3 times I know how it feels to be at 100% confidence & I know how it feels to be at 1% just keep pushing & talk to people or talk to me my inbox is always open if anyone has any questions 👊🏻

Now I’m gonna have a few naughty treats over Xmas & then smash the hell out of it after crimbo lets go 🫶🏻🫶🏻🫶🏻

And shout out to @fredagainagainagainagainagain this song has got me through the wind, rain, sleet & snow powerful 👊🏻

Booking your wedding for 2024,2025 or 2026 .. Entertainment is one of the main elements that sets the atmosphere for whole the day🔥🔥🔥

So let me take you from acoustic sing alongs for all ages in the drinks reception 👉🏻 to a wedding breakfast your guests will always talk about 👉🏻 to turning your evening reception into a nightclub atmosphere you and your guests will never forget it🕺🏻💃🙌🏻❤️

social_posts.post_text:
1 year today since I had my gastric sleeve op that would change my life forever 🙌🏻❤️

Always being a mentally strong, driven person from a young age nothing would ever prepare me for what lockdown would do to my life, nearly loosing my brother to Covid then loosing all of my income for 2 years! Relationships I had built with clients of 15 years, levels I had climbed in 20yrs to come crashing down around me, honestly sent me over the edge I’m not gonna lie I went from 18stone to 26stone in about 2yrs 😳 

I would just eat because I was depressed I became addicted to food on a bigger level, eating more & more, as I mentioned I had always been up an down with my weight but this really sent me too far the other way 😞 I knew I had to do something to save my own life & my wife sat me down snapped me out of this crazy downhill spiral I had fallen into & gave me the kick up the arse I really needed & I’ll never forget that!

I researched into gastric sleeve op’s & other options, then a couple of my good friends made the leap before me, I saw how it changed their lives I thought I need to do this not just for me but for my family, my wife, my little boy. I want to live for as long as I can, We get one life and we don’t get long it’s not just about me anymore so that was it I booked it! 

Thankyou @getsliminturkey & @dr.fikretbeyaz for giving me my life back - Confidence, fitness, drive, determination, happiness I honestly wish I had done this sooner & stopped hesitating for so long 💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻

9stone down & I feel like a new man, I look like a different man it’s crazy my journey is still ongoing & I still have 3 stone till I reach my goal weight but I am more than happy with how the last 12 months have gone 🙏🏻

Thankyou to everyone that’s supported me all the way & thankyou to my pal & trainer @maggsy_pt for giving me his time to help me achieve my fitness goals we ain’t done yet 😉

To any friends, family or followers struggling with weight loss or anything else that is getting them down plz just speak about it!

My inbox is always open & sometimes we all need somebody to talk too!

#weightloss #gastricsleeve #1year #9stonedown #fitness #goals

Been hitting it hard this week 🥊🥊🥊

amazing how much my speed precision and stamina has come on in this last six months 💪🏻

#boxing #strength #stamina #determination #weightloss
I’ll be back out at my fav spot in Spain for a special Valentines performance if your in the area come see me at @olivias_la_cala 🙌🏻❤️🫶🏻

Thankyou to Dr Zabeeh & the @britishhairclinic once again you guys are the best 🙌🏻❤️🫶🏻

3 years since my first transplant on the front of my head & I’ve had amazing results, so have the 40odd people that have been to this brilliant place off the back of my recommendation 🙏🏻

At the time I also discussed the middle/back of my hair as I knew within a couple of years I would probably need that doing too & the guys gave me some great advice - My hair is a big part of my confidence being a performer & Dj not to sure I’m ready for the Denis Roberts look just yet 🤣

So many others suffer with their confidence because of hair loss too & I’m so glad since my first procedure so many people messaged me, spoke up about it & visited BHC 👊🏻

So today I went in for part 2 buzzing for the next few months Thankyou @britishhairclinic 👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻
